name: marie antoinette
description:
Portrait of Marie Antoinette Josèphe Jeanne (2 November 1755 – 16 October 1793)

I redraw the portrait of Marie Antoinette for accepting a challenge in instagram on 27 April 2020 

I choose her because she was a 'woman in fury', a murderous plotter who dreamed of 'Swimming in the blood of the French'. UPS! No. I choose to redraw her in no reason except her punishment in guillotine.

2835 × 3071 | digital drawing on procreate
